SOURCE: https://github.com/kentcdodds/kentcdodds.com/blob/main/content/blog/build-vs-buy-component-libraries-edition.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
---
title: 'Build vs Buy: Component Libraries edition'
date: 2021-02-04
description:
  Some things to think about before you decide to create your own component
  library.
categories:
  - open source
meta:
  keywords:
    - components
    - react
    - angular
    - vue
    - business
    - oss
bannerCloudinaryId: unsplash/photo-1590403183019-8ab6ba58ce50
bannerCredit: Photo by [George Bakos](https://unsplash.com/photos/VDAzcZyjun8)
---
```

