TITLE: Creating an Info Callout in Markdown
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create an informational callout in Markdown using custom HTML-like syntax. The callout contains a note about the purpose of the live stream and its focus on Remix.
SOURCE: https://github.com/kentcdodds/kentcdodds.com/blob/main/content/blog/rsc-with-dan-abramov-and-joe-savona-live-stream.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: markdown
CODE:
```
<callout-info class="aside">
	It should be noted that the objective of this live stream was not to instruct
	you, but to answer my own questions. I realize some folks will wish we spent
	more time explaining some of the concepts and answering other people's
	questions, but we only had time for my own questions. This is also why there
	was such a big focus on Remix as well since I'm a heavy Remix user.
</callout-info>
```

